2. Nf3 Nf6 { Attacking the e4-pawn. } 3. c3
{ Hoping for the cheap trap  3...Nxe4?  4.Qa4+  winning a piece. } 3... e5
{ We just play normal moves.  3...c5  is also possible, and it would transpose to the Sicilian. }
