cxd6 11. Bb5 { The most active way to develop the bishop. } 11... Rhd8
{ Black has no real weaknesses, as d6 is easy to defend. We have ideas to play ...h6 and ...g5 or ...a6. Black is already preferable and went on to win a nice game in 0-1 Vallejo Pons-Carlsen, Sao Paulo/Bilbao 2012. }
