{ Despite defending the e4-pawn, practice has shown that the queen still feels misplaced on this square. }
8... b5 { Immediately starting counterplay. } 9. O-O-O
{ Threatening to take twice on e5. } 9... Qc7
{ White doesn't really have threats, and the queen is misplaced on d3. We want to follow up with ...g6 to cover the g-file. }
