{ The logical follow-up, intending h4 and g5. If  7.g5  hxg5  8.Nxg5  c6  , Black is already better,  as the bishop is on e2, not attacking f7.  And if White tries  9.Bc4  now, we can meet it with  9...O-O  or try to refute White's idea outright with  9...d5!?  10.exd5  Nb6! }
