10. Bd3
{ Reinforcing the center and the e4-pawn. If  10.Rg1  , then  10...g5  is interesting, stopping White's counterplay. }
10... Nf8
{ A typical manoeuver, rerouting the knight to g6. It's not clear what White does next. The position is very unclear. }
