Nxd4 Re8 { Putting more pressure on e4. } 12. Bf4
{ Preparing Qc2 followed by Rad1.   12.e5?  doesn't work because of  12...Bxg2  13.exf6  Rxe1+  14.Qxe1  Qxf6  , and  the d4-knight is hanging. }
