12. Nf3 Nd7 { ...Nc5 is a real threat. } 13. O-O
{ This careless move is actually a blunder. } 13... Nc5
{ And suddenly, White cannot protect the b3-pawn.  14.Qc2  transposes to the 13.Qc2 variation. }
